{"tid":752960,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國毒疫苗　波多野結衣「先知」被讚爆","createTime":"2018-07-23T08:37:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-24T12:20:24.000Z","uid":184679,"like":358,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":68,"replies":[{"pid":"2718c7aeba5609ba0d4c1cab4ba02e60860565cd","tid":752960,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:37:29.000Z","msg":"中國爆發疫苗造假案，引發民眾驚恐，甚至湧入美國駐華大使館的微博，希望美國總統川普伸出援手。不過中國假疫苗已非首次，2年前疫苗出現問題時，日本知名AV女優波多野結衣就曾氣噗噗地在微博發文，「有壞蛋在中國大量秘密銷售假疫苗？太可氣了！」如今這篇發文再被翻出來，中國網友感嘆原來日本人2年前就知道。<br />\n<br />\n波多野結衣2016年3月底時，以中、日文抨擊中國假疫苗，還配上做出生氣樣的臉蛋，如今中國再爆假疫苗，許多網友紛紛來朝聖留言「這麼早就知道了厲害」、「就疫苗的事，你看看中國的星們有幾個站出來說話的，他們真的不如這位小姐」、「波多老師就知道了」、「德藝雙馨」、「AV界良心女優」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180723/1396900/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180723%2F1396900%2F&d=dhnmO4SUVKWMyUZrxg720b%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=0254d09e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180723%2F1396900%2F&h=575f4588\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180723/1396900/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180723/640_7704b4aa6af830fe7fb3bbd2643033b8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180723%2F640_7704b4aa6af830fe7fb3bbd2643033b8.jpg&h=fbb16a63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"40001c88ca20ebecc20171841f4c03d6593a96b4","tid":752960,"uid":127929,"like":71,"dislike":5,"score":66,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:42:57.000Z","msg":"有得屌我屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f4cb0be5392a2d1553fc4483a8dd8795de9120e","tid":752960,"uid":176366,"like":95,"dislike":0,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-23T08:44:15.000Z","msg":"太可惡了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b